    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320730/extras/b962171349dcc08e87f5494571977ff3.poster.avif?t=1729276783\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320730/extras/b962171349dcc08e87f5494571977ff3.webm?t=1729276783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320730/extras/b962171349dcc08e87f5494571977ff3.mp4?t=1729276783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a futuristic sky-city teeming with glitchy robots in NEON DEATH DROP, an action game about a gay go-go boy who must use his fierce dance moves to save the world. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GROUND IS YOUR PLAYGROUND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manipulate floor tiles by making them move, grow, or even disappear</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320730/extras/9ae8e7b95e91cc52aa0ba7c88984384f.poster.avif?t=1729276783\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320730/extras/9ae8e7b95e91cc52aa0ba7c88984384f.webm?t=1729276783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320730/extras/9ae8e7b95e91cc52aa0ba7c88984384f.mp4?t=1729276783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SLAY THE BOTS DOWN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies by knocking them into pits and watch them drop dead</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320730/extras/b3da1fae8675a74b84d0713ded81e9e9.poster.avif?t=1729276783\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320730/extras/b3da1fae8675a74b84d0713ded81e9e9.webm?t=1729276783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320730/extras/b3da1fae8675a74b84d0713ded81e9e9.mp4?t=1729276783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMBO YOUR CHOREO</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine dynamic dance moves to perform spectacular takedowns and see your TIP$ go through the roof!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge waves of projectiles in bullet hell mayhem </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat big bad bosses by countering their attacks </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore sprawling cityscapes and enjoy neon-tastic vistas </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden treasures to beef up your abilities  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy hours of sassy voiceover as you unfold the story </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restore order to the city and become the fabulous hero you were born to be</p></li></ul>",
